-- Greek ruling party lawmaker says PM must scrap referendum plan
-- 
-- Thu Nov 3, 2011 2:59am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/11/03/us-greece-idUSTRE7A216C20111103

 

 ATHENS  (Reuters) - Another Greek ruling party lawmaker joined on Thursday the chorus of party members urging Prime Minister George Papandreou to withdraw his plan for a referendum on a euro rescue package. 
 "He should withdraw the proposal, immediately, today," Mimis Androulakis told Antenna TV. (Reporting by  Ingrid Melander  and Harry Papachristou)